    <item>
      <title>南非财政部长表示国家工资待遇已达上限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/south-african-finance-minister-signals-state-wage-offer-at-limit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非财政部长表示，通胀放缓后，政府无法保证上个月向公务员提出的 4.7% 工资增长幅度会进一步增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/south-african-finance-minister-signals-state-wage-offer-at-limit</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 14:11:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国经济：GDP 增长 2.8%，失业救济申请下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/us-economy-gdp-grows-at-2-8-jobless-claims-fall-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周，美国失业救济申请人数下降 2,000 人，降至 213,000 人，而美国经济在第三季度保持稳健增长，国内生产总值年化增长率为 2.8%。迈克尔·麦基在彭博电视台上对这些数字进行了分析。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-27/us-economy-gdp-grows-at-2-8-jobless-claims-fall-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:59:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币山寨币在创纪录的涨势中未能跟上比特币的步伐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/crypto-altcoins-fail-to-keep-pace-with-bitcoin-during-record-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管本月在比特币创纪录的上涨趋势中，山寨币的流入量有所增加，但 2021 年加密货币泡沫的阴影仍然笼罩着该行业的大部分领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/crypto-altcoins-fail-to-keep-pace-with-bitcoin-during-record-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:56:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞信洗钱案被推翻，瑞银被判无罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ubs-acquitted-over-credit-suisse-criminal-money-laundering-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士信贷因未能阻止可卡因交易商利润洗钱而被定罪，该判决在其一名前雇员因该案被判有罪死亡后于 2022 年被瑞士上诉法院推翻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/ubs-acquitted-over-credit-suisse-criminal-money-laundering-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 13:22:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电池制造商 Morrow 呼吁明确关键贷款条款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/battery-maker-morrow-calls-norway-to-rule-on-make-or-break-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威的 Morrow Batteries AS 正面临生存危机，该公司正在等待政府资金批准，而这项资金对于吸引投资者进入因瑞典初创公司 Northvolt AB 倒闭而受到重创的行业至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/battery-maker-morrow-calls-norway-to-rule-on-make-or-break-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Brookfield 放弃以 68 亿美元收购制药商 Grifols 的提议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/brookfield-drops-6-8-billion-offer-to-buy-drugmaker-grifols</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布鲁克菲尔德资产管理有限公司 (Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.) 放弃了收购 Grifols SA 的计划，结束了为期数月的收购这家西班牙血浆公司的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/brookfield-drops-6-8-billion-offer-to-buy-drugmaker-grifols</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 12:57:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
